- DescriptionMaking FMPXMLRESULT format XML from PDO. For FMPXMLREUSLT, see http://www.filemaker.com/11help/html/import_export.16.34.html- Usage1. include_once('PDO2FMPXMLRESULT.class.php');2. $xml = new pdo2fmxml();3. Get meta infomation from PDO, insert to $xml by addMetaData()4. Get records from PDO, insert to $xml by addRecordObject() / addAllRecordsObject()5. echo($xml->saveXML());See more information, PDO2FMPXMLRESULT.class.php- Demo & Resultsqlite> .tablessoftwaresqlite> .schema softwareCREATE TABLE "software" ( id TEXT,name TEXT,release DATE,version NUMERIC);sqlite> select * from software;id|name|release|version1|FileMaker Pro|2010/4/7|112|FileMaker Pro|2009/1/6|10% ./examples.php <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><FMPXMLRESULT xmlns="">  <ERRORCODE>0</ERRORCODE>  <PRODUCT BUILD="09/11/2011" NAME="PDO-Data to FMPXMLRESULT" VERSION="1.0.0"/>  <DATABASE DATEFORMAT="MM/dd/yyyy" LAYOUT="from_PDO_Database" NAME="from_PDO_Database" RECORDS="2" TIMEFORMAT="HH:mm:ss"/>  <METADATA>    <FIELD EMPTYOK="YES" MAXREPEAT="1" NAME="id" TYPE="TEXT"/>    <FIELD EMPTYOK="YES" MAXREPEAT="1" NAME="name" TYPE="TEXT"/>    <FIELD EMPTYOK="YES" MAXREPEAT="1" NAME="release" TYPE="DATE"/>    <FIELD EMPTYOK="YES" MAXREPEAT="1" NAME="version" TYPE="NUMBER"/>  </METADATA>  <RESULTSET FOUND="2">    <ROW MODID="0" RECORDID="1">      <COL>        <DATA>1</DATA>      </COL>      <COL>        <DATA>FileMaker Pro</DATA>      </COL>      <COL>        <DATA>2010/04/07</DATA>      </COL>      <COL>        <DATA>11</DATA>      </COL>    </ROW>    <ROW MODID="0" RECORDID="2">      <COL>        <DATA>2</DATA>      </COL>      <COL>        <DATA>FileMaker Pro</DATA>      </COL>      <COL>        <DATA>2009/01/06</DATA>      </COL>      <COL>        <DATA>10</DATA>      </COL>    </ROW>  </RESULTSET></FMPXMLRESULT>- LicneseCopyright (c) 2011,2012 Hiroaki TOMIDA <tomida at hiroakio.org>All rights reserved.Redistribution a